snippet.title: Dauntless - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Dauntless is a co-op, action RPG coming to PC in 2017.
Sign up now at http://PlayDauntless.com

Discover a shattered world, forge powerful weapons, and hunt the ferocious behemoths threatening our survival.
